        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years or old;

          -  Clinical diagnosis of acute myeloid leukemia (AML);

          -  Availabe records of MICM and NGS results at diagnosis;

          -  Be going to receive allo-HSCT.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Active malignancy;

          -  Pregnant or breast feeding women.
